headlines.description: Mohamed Salah's opener seconds after Aleksandar Mitrovic had a goal ruled put Liverpool ahead, before Xherdan Shaqiri ensured victory.
headlines.shortLinkText: Liverpool see off Fulham in controversial win

headlines.description: Chelsea maintain their unbeaten start to the Premier League campaign despite failing to seal all three points following 0-0 draw against Everton.

headlines.description: Ivan Cavaleiro's first half goal following a mistake from Granit Xhaka was cancelled out late on by Henrikh Mkhitaryan.
headlines.shortLinkText: Arsenal winless run continues after Wolves draw

headlines.description: David Silva, Sergio Aguero and Ilkay Gundogan scored as Manchester City took the derby spoils despite Anthony Martial's penalty.
headlines.shortLinkText: Silva, Aguero, Gundogan seal City win in derby
